# Dataset x Node Support Matrix (Dataset View)

Dataset-oriented view. Empty cell means not supported for that dataset/profile mapping.

| Dataset (Profile) | get_data | curate | label.normalize | label.ic50 | split | featurize / use | preprocess.features | select.features | train | train.tdc | analyze.stats | analyze.eda | explain |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| flash, qm9, ysi, pah (`reg_local_csv`) | `local_csv` | `properties` (+ optional `smiles_column`, `dedupe_strategy`, `keep_all_columns`) |  |  | `holdout/cv/nested_holdout_cv` + `random/scaffold` | `use.curated_features`, `featurize.rdkit`, `featurize.morgan` | Yes (requires feature input) | Yes (requires preprocess + feature input) | `random_forest`, `svm`, `decision_tree`, `xgboost`, `ensemble`, `dl_*` |  |  |  | Yes |
| chembl (`reg_chembl_ic50`) | `chembl` | `properties: standard_value`, `keep_all_columns` |  | Yes | `holdout/cv/nested_holdout_cv` + `random/scaffold` | `featurize.lipinski` + `featurize.rdkit` (rdkit input required) | Yes (requires feature input) | Yes (requires preprocess + feature input) | `random_forest`, `svm`, `decision_tree`, `xgboost`, `ensemble`, `dl_*` |  | Yes | Yes | Yes |
| pgp, ara (`clf_local_csv`) | `local_csv` | `properties`, `smiles_column`, `dedupe_strategy`, `label_column` | Optional (required if target not already binary) |  | `holdout/cv/nested_holdout_cv` + `random/scaffold` | `catboost_classifier`/`dl_*`: one of `use.curated_features`, `featurize.rdkit`, `featurize.morgan`; `chemprop`: none required | Yes for non-chemprop (requires feature input) | Yes for non-chemprop (requires preprocess + feature input) | `catboost_classifier`, `chemprop`, `dl_*` |  |  |  | Yes* (chemprop explain is skipped) |
| pgp_tdc_benchmark (`clf_tdc_benchmark`) |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  | `catboost_classifier` |  |  |  |

## Notes

- `train` and `train.tdc` are mutually exclusive.
- `train.tdc` must be terminal (last node).
- `split` must appear before `preprocess.features`, `select.features`, `train`, and `explain`.
- `chemprop` cannot be paired with `preprocess.features`/`select.features` in DOE validation.
- Runtime warns and skips explainability for chemprop.
- `clf_tdc_benchmark` uses a `train.tdc`-only pipeline (no `get_data` node).
